title: JKPSC Notification 2026 - Apply Online for 29 Professor Posts
description: The Jammu & Kashmir Public Service Commission (JKPSC) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 29 Professor Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, DNB, M.Sc., MD/MS, and Ph.D. can apply for the JKPSC Notification 2026. The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
